title: Russia tightens grip on Ukraine's Donbas Region | DW News
description: Moscow has set it sights on gaining control of the Donbas, Ukraine's industrial heartland. Russian troops are attempting to encircle Ukrainian forces by seizing key highways in the region.|Ukraine says 50 towns in the region came under shelling Thursday, which killed at least 9 people. With Russian troops gaining ground, residents here see no escape in sight.|Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy is frustrated that the European Union has struggled to reach a consensus on its latest sanctions against Russia.|"How many more weeks will the European Union try to agree on a sixth package?" Zelenskyy said during a late-night address.|Ukrainian authorities there are facing a massive undertaking in investigating crimes committed by Russian soldiers. More than 13.000 cases of crimes against civilians, including the murder, rape and torture are being investigated. In the Kyiv region even months after the occupation, new crimes are discovered every day.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russland #Putin

title: IAS couple dog walking row: Mahua, Omar question transfers to Arunachal, Ladakh | Internet in splits
description: A massive controversy has erupted in the national capital after a picture of an IAS couple walking their dog in Thyagraj Stadium went viral. Sanjeev Khirwar and Rinku Dugga, both 1994 batch officers of the AGMUT cadre, were forcing athletes to finish their training by 7 PM, so that they could bring their dog to the facility for daily evening walk. The Ministry of Home Affairs has now transferred the couple to Arunachal Pradesh and Ladakh. However, TMC MP Mahua Moitra and NC Leader Omar Abdullah have slammed this punishment posting claiming that it was demoralising to the people there to be given the impression that officers only get sent as a punishment. Meanwhile, the internet is in splits as the 2 officers have been sent to opposite ends of the country. Memes went viral asking who will take care of the dog amid all of this. Watch this video for more details.|#IASCouple #Dog #ThyagrajStadium #SanjeevKhirwar #RinkuDugga #ArunachalPradesh #Ladakh #Delhi #MHA #Centre #DelhiGovernment #ModiGovernment

title: Imran Khan heaps praise on India amid fuel price hike in Pak; Lauds Modi govtâ€™s strategy
description: Former Pakistan PM Imran Khan has once again praised India. Hitting out at the Shehbaz Sharif government for hiking fuel prices in Pakistan, Imran lauded India for being able to reduce fuel prices amid cheaper oil from Russia. In a series of tweets, Imran said the highest price hike is the price Pakistan will pay for the incompetent and insensitive government. "In contrast India, strategic ally of the U.S., has managed to reduce fuel prices by Pkr 25 per litre by buying cheaper oil from Russia. Now our nation will suffer another massive dose of inflation at the hands of this cabal of crooks." tweeted Imran. The Shehbaz Sharif government in Pakistan increased the prices of all petroleum products by Pak rupees (PKR) 30/litre to reduce fuel subsidies. The highest-ever increase in the prices of all petroleum products in one go is aimed at impressing the International Monetary Fund. Watch this video for more details.|#Pakistan #ImranKhan #FuelPrices #India #NarendraModiGovernment #ShehbazSharifGovernment #PKR #Petrol #Diesel #Petroleum

title: Fakta-fakta Sungai Aare Swiss, Lokasi Hilangnya Emmeril Anak Sulung Ridwan Kamil
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Dikabarkan anak sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz (Eril), hilang terseret arus Sungai Aare, Bern, Swiss, Kamis (26/5/2022).||||Dalam keterangan resminya, adik Ridwan Kamil, Elpi Nazmuzaman menuturkan kejaidan berawal saat Eril berenang di Sungai Aare, Bern, bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Berikut sejumlah fakta mengenai Sungai Aare lokasi Emmeril terseret arus:||||Mengutip situs web Kota Bern, Jumat (27/5/2022), Sungai Aare bukan lokasi asing bagi warga lokal maupun turis.||||Baca Juga Kronologi Anak Ridwan Kamil Diduga Terseret Arus Saat Berenang di Sungai Aaree Swiss di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293083/kronologi-anak-ridwan-kamil-diduga-terseret-arus-saat-berenang-di-sungai-aaree-swiss||||Sungai Terpanjang di Swiss||||Dengan panjang 288 kilometer, Aare adalah sungai terpanjang yang mengalir sepenuhnya di Swiss bermuara di gletser Aar Bawah dan Atas di Bernese Oberland dan rutenya ke utara berakhir di Koblenz.||||Warisan Budaya Takbenda Swiss||||Sejak 2017, berenang di Sungai Aare merupakan tradisi dan karenanya masuk daftar warisan budaya tak benda UNESCO.||||Rekor Dunia Arung Jeram||||Rekor dunia untuk arung jeram Sungai Aare dibuat di Bern pada 2012, ketika total 1.268 orang secara bersamaan mengarungi sungai tersebut dengan perahu karet, dari Kiesen ke Eichholz.||||Lokasi Tradisi Zibeleschwmme||||Zibeleschwmme merupakan tradisi berenang di Sungai Aare saat musim dingin. Setelah berenang, mereka pun menghangatkan diri dengan suara karnaval "musik Guggen," teh panas, dan sup.||||Bagi Perenang Berpengalaman||||Berenang di Aare direkomendasikan hanya untuk perenang berpengalaman.||||Video Editor: Rengga||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293087/fakta-fakta-sungai-aare-swiss-lokasi-hilangnya-emmeril-anak-sulung-ridwan-kamil

title: Kondisi Terkini Pencarian Anak Ridwan Kamil di Swiss
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV   - Saat mendapatkan informasi mengenai hilangnya Emmeril Khan Mumtadz atau Eril, sang ayah Ridwan Kamil yang sedang berada di Inggris segera menuntaskan kegiatannya dan langsung menuju Swiss.||||"Pada saat beliau berkegiatan beliau mendapatkan kabar dari keluarga mengenai hilang kontak Eril dan keluarga pada Kamis 26 Mei 2022. Setelah menerima kabar tersebut bapak Gubernur Jabar menuntaskan kegiatan di Inggris dan ke Swiss. Ridwan Kamil tiba di Bern, Swiss, Jumat (26/5/2022) pukul 1 waktu setempat."ujar Kepala Bagian Materi dan Komunikasi Pimpinan Biro Administrasi Pimpinan Pemprov Jabar Akhmad Taufiqurrachman.||||Baca Juga Anak Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz Hilang Teseret Arus Sungai di Swiss! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292998/anak-ridwan-kamil-emmeril-khan-mumtadz-hilang-teseret-arus-sungai-di-swiss||||Pihak kepolisian Swiss melanjutkan proses pencarian dengan jangkauan yang lebih luas mulai pukul 9 pagi waktu setempat.||||"Kepolisian Swiss melanjutkan jangkauan pencarian pada jumat 9 pagi Swiss. Kami atas nama Pemda Jabar sangat berharap dan ajak masyarakat agar kang Eril ditemukan sehat. Kami mengajak rekan-rekan media menjaga privasi bapak gubernur."ucap Akhmad Taufiqurrachman.||||Video Editor: Febi|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293085/kondisi-terkini-pencarian-anak-ridwan-kamil-di-swiss

title: Plan A Trip To Unexplored GUREZ VALLEY In Kashmir Now ğŸ˜ | Garima's Good Life
description: Hi Friends|I recently went to Gurez Valley in Kashmir for a weekend with my friend Ritu. It's a must visit place. I took a direct Spicejet flight from Mumbai to Srinagar and then drove 140 kms from Srinagar to Gurez. It's about 5 hours drive. I stayed at Pine Tree Resort which was a nice and cosy accommodation. Gurez valley is accessible only in summers. So plan your trip now :)|You can do the following activities in Gurez Valley |1. Visit the last village of India near Pakistan border TULAIL|2. Enjoy camping near River Kishanganga.|3. Visit the army cafe LOG HUT CAFE for great food|4. Enjoy local tractor ride and see the village and farms|5. Visit Habba Khatoon peak for fresh water spring|The overall budget for this trip can cost you from Rs15,000 onwards excluding flight fares, depending on your choice of hotel and activities. You can book your tour through Tour The Kashmir. Sharing my guide Javid's number  +91-8491850068|https://www.instagram.com/tour_the_kashmir/|http://www.adventuregulmarg.com/|This place is a virgin and untouched beauty of Kashmir. It was absolutely safe and the people were very nice. Hope this video helps to plan your trip to this paradise on earth.|Also watch my other videos from Kashmir|Travel Guidelines - https://youtu.be/ZxCDnO3caIE|GULMARG Tour Guide - https://youtu.be/8tzokWbTo4A|Pashmina shopping haul - https://youtu.be/mp8JGFjhskk|Exploring Srinagar - https://youtu.be/O--fUFuzOYE|Love|Garima|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|If you are new to my Channel, Do subscribe to https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZXhZeAbY4LYynmzVe-IQ4w|Follow me on Instagram @garimasgoodlife|https://www.instagram.com/garimasgoodlife/?hl=en|Join my Facebook page|https://www.facebook.com/garimasgoodlife/|Email me on Garimasgoodlife@gmail.comHi Friends

So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.|About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:|--------------------------------------------------------------------|The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. title: PM Modi inaugurates Bharat Drone Mahotsav at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi
description: Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi will inaugurate India's biggest Drone Festival - Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 - on 27 May 2022 at 10 AM at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi.|Prime Minister will also interact with kisan drone pilots, witness open-air drone demonstrations and interact with startups in the drone exhibition centre.|Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 is a two day event and is being held on 27th and 28th May. Over 1600 delegates comprising government officials, foreign diplomats, armed forces, central armed police forces, PSUs, private companies and drone startups etc. will participate in the Mahotsav. More than 70 exhibitors will display various use cases of drones at the exhibition. Mahotsav will also witness a virtual award of drone pilot certificates, product launches, panel discussions, flying demonstrations, display of a Made in India Drone Taxi prototype, among others.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! ğŸ””||||Follow us to stay updated:||||â–º Download the NM App: http://nm4.in/dnldapp||â–º Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/narendramodi|#BharatDroneMahotsav  #PragatiMaidan #NewDelhi

title: 'Deceit in garb of ceasefire': Indian Army tears into Pak for pushing terror in Kashmir
description: Indian Army has hit out at Pakistan after three infiltrators were gunned near LoC in J&K's Kupwara yesterday. The Indian Army said that exporting terrorism in J&K has been a state policy of Pakistan for last three decades. Three heavily-armed terrorists from Pakistan were intercepted and killed by the forces in Kupwara. There has been a surge in infiltration attempts from Pakistan since the last many weeks along the LoC in J&K. The surge in terror infiltrations comes at a time when a ceasefire is in place on the border between India and Pakistan. Watch the full video for more.|#India #Pakistan #IndianArmy #LoC #Ceasefire #Terrorists #Terror #Kupwara #InfiltrationBid #JammuAndKashmir

title: Pak buckles under IMF pressure as Sharif govt hikes petrol and diesel prices by Rs 30
description: Cash strapped Pakistan increased the price of petroleum products by Rs 30 per litre. After the increase, the price of one litre petrol will be at Rs 179.85 and diesel at Rs 174.15 in Pakistan. Similarly, the kerosene in Pakistan now costs  Rs 155.95 per litre and light diesel at Rs 148.41. Pakistan finance minister Miftah Ismail made the announcement at a press conference last evening. The decision was announced a day after the talks between the pakistan govt & IMF failed to reach an agreement on an economic bailout and the IMF staff-level agreement for the revival of the usd 6 billion programme ended. Watch the full video for more.|#Pakistan #ShehbazSharif #Petrol #Diesel #IMF

title: Ratusan CPNS yang Mengundurkan Diri Rugikan Negara dan Bisa Didenda Ratusan juta
description: Sebanyak 105 CPNS dilaporkan mengundurkan diri meski sudah lulus pada tahun 2021 lalu. Kepala Biro Hukum, Humas, dan Kerja Sama BKN Satya Pratama mengatakan salah satu alasan pengunduran diri ini dikarenakan masalah gaji.|||Satya menyebut mereka merasa gaji sebagai PNS yang ditawarkan terlalu kecil. Terkait hal ini, para peserta yang mengundurkan diri akan diberikan sanksi.|||Sanksi tersebut yakni peserta tidak boleh melamar pada penerimaan ASN periode berikutnya. Selain itu, peserta juga dapat dikenakan sanksi berupa denda di instansi masing-masing.|||Simak informasinya dalam video berikut.|||Penulis: Fitria Chusna Farisa, Adhyasta Dirgantara, Issha Harumma||Penulis Naskah: Anasthasya||Host: Anasthasya||Video Editor: Dina Rahmawati||Produser: Elizabeth Prillia Yahya Carvallo|||#CPNS #NewsUpdate #JernihkanHarapan #Kompascom

title: Suzuki V-Strom 250 SX Review | Adventure Ready or A Comfortable Tourer?
description: One of the biggest surprise two-wheeler launches of 2022 is the Suzuki V-Strom 250 SX. The V-Strom SX is the first affordable ADV two-wheeler offering from the Japanese two-wheeler giant for the Indian market and also its third 250cc motorcycle. The Suzuki V-Strom SX is powered by the same 250cc engine as seen on its other 250cc siblings and even the gear ratios are identical. What is different though is the styling, the V-Strom 250 looks like a scaled-down version of the bigger V-Strom 1050 and the V-Strom 650.Â |The new Suzuki 250cc ADV bike features LED headlight, all-digital instrument cluster with Bluetooth connectivity for navigation, call and message alerts and even an external USB charger. While the bike has the visual appeal of a proper adventure bike, the Suzuki V-Strom doesnâ€™t have the kit to justify the V-Strom name. The suspension travel is similar to its road-spec offerings and it doesnâ€™t even get dual-channel ABS. We head out for a 230km road trip from Dharamshala to Manali to find out if the V-Strom 250 SX is a proper adventure tourer or if it's just a sudo ADV bike.Â |HostÂ  - Arun Mohan Nadar|DOP - Neeraj Panwar|Editor - Harshvardhan Rathod|More details on the 2023 KTM 390 Duke - https://www.zigwheels.com/newbikes/Suzuki/v-strom-250Â |Donâ€™t forget to also check out the following videos on ZigWheels:|Yamaha MT-15 Version 2.0 Road Test: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jorinâ€¦Â |Royal Enfield Himalayan 450 Incoming: https://youtu.be/x89gE_8wUp0Â |2022 KTM 390 Adventure Review: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H1fxUâ€¦Â |Scram Attack - RE Scram 411 vs Yezdi Scrambler - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LtesldOMTI8

title: SARWENDAH PENGEN MAKAN SOTO BETAWI, BETRAND AJAK JAJAN DI LUAR | The Onsu Family

Menurut pendapat tim di dekat komplek ada soto betawi yang rasanya enak banget. Jadi langsung deh Betrand dan Bunda kesana, naik motor aja ya kan deket hehe. Gak lupa juga pakai helm nya. Eh tiba-tiba Thalia dan Thania mau nyusul nih. Wah makin seru aja. Penasarankan dengan keseruannya? title: Anak Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz Hilang Teseret Arus Sungai di Swiss!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Anak sulung Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz atau biasa dipanggil Eril mengalami musibah di Bern, Swiss pada 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss.||||Musibah hilangnya anak sulung Ridwan Kamil tersebut terjadi saat Eril berenang di sungai Aaree, Bern bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Saat ingin naik ke permukaan, Eril terseret arus sungai yang cukup deras yang sebelumnya sempat mendapat bantuan dari kawannya.||||Kejadian tersebut terjadi pada tanggal 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss dengan kondisi cuaca cerah.||||Keluarga dari Ridwan Kamil sendiri saat itu sedang berada di Swiss untuk mencari sekolah untuk Eril yang akan melanjutkan ke jenjang S2.||||Saat kejadian, Pak Ridwan Kamil sedang berada di Inggris dalam kegiatan pemerintahan di luar negeri bersama delegasi dari Pemprov Jawa Barat. ||||----||||Jangan lewatkan streaming Kompas TV live 24 jam non stop di https://www.kompas.tv/live  agar kamu semua tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia.||||Subscribe juga channel YouTube Kompas TV  di https://www.youtube.com/c/kompastv dan aktifkan lonceng supaya kamu dapat notifikasi video terbaru langsung. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292998/anak-ridwan-kamil-emmeril-khan-mumtadz-hilang-teseret-arus-sungai-di-swiss

title: Scottie Scheffler headlines eight-way tie after 18 holes at Charles Schwab | 2022
description: In the opening round of the 2022 Charles Schwab Challenge, eight players turned in 4-under 66â€™s to tie for the lead heading into Friday.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Five of the top 10 players in the world will tee it up this week at Colonial Country Club in Fort Worth, Texas, for the Charles Schwab Challenge. title: Kata Jokowi soal Kepemimpinan Gibran Rakabuming Raka sebagai Wali Kota Solo
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Joko Widodo tak berkomentar banyak soal sepak terjang anaknya Gibran Rakabuming Raka sebagai Wali Kota Solo.||||Hal ini disampaikan Jokowi saat kunjungan di Taman Kota Balekambang, Solo, Jawa Tengah pada Kamis (26/5)||||Presiden Jokowi mengaku sibuk karena pekerjaannya juga banyak sekali.||||"Waduh, saya enggak ngikuti. Tugas dan pekerjaan saya sendiri banyak sekali," kata Jokowi||||Baca Juga Ini Momen Presiden Jokowi Lepas Masker di Pasar dan Bagikan Bantuan ke Pedagang di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292986/ini-momen-presiden-jokowi-lepas-masker-di-pasar-dan-bagikan-bantuan-ke-pedagang||||Ditanya soal rencana pengembangan Taman Balekambang sebagai pusat kebudayaan di Solo, Presiden Jokowi meminta wartawan untuk menanyakan langsung ke Wali Kota.||||"Tanya ke Pak Wali. Saya enggak mengikuti karena yang saya ikuti itu 514 kabupaten/kota, 34 provinsi," ujar Jokowi.||||Meski begitu, Jokowi menegaskan bahwa pemerintah akan selalu mendukung semua bentuk pengembangan seni budaya di tanah air.||||Video Editor: Ian Andrian||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293004/kata-jokowi-soal-kepemimpinan-gibran-rakabuming-raka-sebagai-wali-kota-solo

title: The Ending Of Top Gun: Maverick Explained
description: After 35 years of waiting, "Top Gun: Maverick" arrived in the summer movie season of 2022. It launched a new story in the saga of Pete "Maverick" Mitchell, the hotshot pilot from the original film who's older but not necessarily wiser, still flying planes as far and as fast as he can. An intriguing blend of old and new, "Top Gun: Maverick" is an attempt to recapture the spirit of the original film while also pushing things further and higher. While the ending doesn't have many big twists, there's still a lot of thematic importance that you might have missed. title: How 'Everything Everywhere All At Once' Pulled Off Its Kung Fu Fight Scenes | Movies Insider
description: The fight scenes in "Everything Everywhere All at Once" put a fresh spin on classic kung fu movies. We spoke with stunt coordinator Timothy Eulich and fight choreographers Andy and Brian Le about how the movie's most impressive action sequences came together.|Timothy, Andy, and Brian worked with directing duo Daniel Kwan and Daniel Scheinert, aka the Daniels, to plan and execute the film's fight scenes on a tight budget and shooting schedule, shooting almost entirely within the confines of a single warehouse building in Southern California. Here, they talk about the inspirations and references they pulled from in choreographing the action in "Everything Everywhere," from classic Hong Kong movies and Jackie Chan action flicks to break dancing and parkour. |Timothy has worked as a stunt coordinator and performer on TV series like "Westworld" and "Stranger Things" and films like "Spider-Man: No Way Home" and "Cobra Kai." Previously, he collaborated with the Daniels on their A24-released "Swiss Army Man," starring Paul Dano and Daniel Radcliffe.|Andy and Brian are the brothers and self-taught martial artists behind the popular YouTube channel Martial Club. They appear in several scenes of "Everything Everywhere" as both actors and stunt doubles, most memorably opposite Michelle Yeoh in the IRS trophy fight. Previously, the siblings worked on Marvel's "Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings," with Andy playing the Death Dealer in the film.|"Everything Everywhere All At Once" is out in theaters. title: Russia 'will not win' war in Ukraine, says German Chancellor Scholz | DW News
description: German Chancellor Scholz may have felt like he's the lonely leader of the West. Scholz delivered the closing address at the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, a meeting where the globe's economic and political leaders traditionally rub elbows, meet and greet. Not this year.|Scholz was the only leader of all the G-7 countries who traveled to Davos this year. And that jury is still on what being the only one means or symbolizes.  The world's leaders, especially in Europe and the US, are dealing with the war in Ukraine, broken global supply chains and soaring inflation.   |That didn't keep Ukrainian president Zelensky from zooming with the movers and shakers in Davos. Still, among Western leaders, Scholz was the other one who bothered to show up.  |Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Donbas #WEF #Zelenskyy

title: On the fence, Justin Thomas salvages par
description: In the opening round of the 2022 Charles Schwab Challenge, Justin Thomas pulls his tee shot left at the par-4 3rd hole, ending up a few feet from a fence. Limited with his swing, Thomas punches his second through a gap in the trees and finds the fairway. He pitches his third to 7 feet, and makes the putt to salvage par.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Five of the top 10 players in the world will tee it up this week at Colonial Country Club in Fort Worth, Texas, for the Charles Schwab Challenge. After missing his first cut since October 2021 at last weekâ€™s PGA Championship, World No.1 Scottie Scheffler will be hoping for a return to the incredible form that has seen him win four times already this season. Defending champion Jason Kokrak will make his return to Texas, as will RBC Heritage winner Jordan Spieth, who narrowly missed out on a victory last year, after shooting 73 in the final round. Fresh from his record-equaling comeback victory at the PGA Championship, Justin Thomas will be full of confidence in Fort Worth, however, heâ€™ll have to significantly improve upon his 2021 performance, which saw him finish 12 shots off the lead in T43, if he is going to taste victory for a second week in a row.||||||Welcome to the official YouTube channel of the PGA TOUR. title: Obesity and corporate greed | DW Documentary
description: Doctors predict that by 2030, half of the world's population will be overweight or obese. An epidemic of obesity is causing a rapid rise in diabetes, cardiovascular disease, and cancer. It's becoming the biggest health challenge worldwide.|Why has no country managed to stop this epidemic? The food industry and government authorities say it's due to a lack of individual self-discipline. Is this true? Or is it the result of collective failure -- a symptom of a liberal society that abhors obesity, yet produces people who are overweight. Is society itself to blame for this situation?|Around the world, politicians, priests, doctors, and average people are standing up to multinational food corporations. They want to take back control of their nutrition and their bodies -- and they're using the law, scientific evidence, and political activism to correct the claim that people who are obese have only themselves to blame. These critics focus on sugary drinks that can be as addictive as some hard drugs; misleading advertising directed at children and low-income people; governments that turn a blind eye to junk-food companies; and lobbying that pushes the limits of legality.|These people say that a "hostile takeover" of our food has been |underway for four decades, and they're demanding new legislation to put a stop to it. This documentary investigates how Chile is leading the way in this struggle. Which country will be the next to confront the big food corporations in the name of public health?|#documentary #dwdocumentary #obesity|______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: The Earth Is Actually Weirder Than You Think
description: Watch the new season of MinuteBody - and get access to both CuriosityStream and Nebula - at https://curiositystream.com/minuteearth|Most of Earthâ€™s land is currently in the northern hemisphere because we happen to exist in a time where uneven heating in the mantle has pushed many continental plates northward.|LEARN MORE|**************|To learn more about this topic, start your googling with these keywords: |- Continental drift: An early theory of land movement that posited that the continents floated on the ocean bed. |- Tetrahedral hypothesis: An early theory that attempted to explain the arrangement of Earthâ€™s continents and oceans based on the geometry of a tetrahedron.|- Plate tectonics: The generally accepted theory that the Earthâ€™s surface is made up of a series of tectonic plates that slowly move around on top of the mantle.|- Pangea: The most recent supercontinent to form on Earth, during the late Paleozoic era. |- Great Rift Valley: A series of contiguous geographic trenches between two tectonic plates where humans first evolved.|- Aurica: A potential future supercontinent predicted to form in about 200 million years.|SUPPORT title: Russian forces tighten grip on eastern Donbas region | DW News
description: Russia is intensifying its campaign in Ukraine's eastern Donbas region, launching attacks on dozens of towns in Luhansk and Donetsk. The key industrial city of Severodonetsk is in growing danger of becoming completely surrounded. Having failed to capture the Ukrainian capital Kyiv and its second largest city Kharkiv, Moscow has focused on smaller objectives. |Ukrainian President Zelenskyy is demanding more heavy weaponry from the west â€“ describing the situation in Donbas as 'extremely difficult.'|German Chancellor Olaf Scholz has said that Russia's President Vladimir Putin cannot be allowed to win the war in Ukraine. |In an address to the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, Scholz repeated his country's support for Ukraine, but did not address Kyiv's demands for more heavy wepons. title: How 'Jack', 'John', 'Alpha' & 'Golf' helped NIA to send Yasin Malik to jail for life | Inside Story
description: Jack', 'John' and 'Alpha' were among the NIA's protected witnesses who helped nail banned JKLF chief Yasin Malik. These names were given to important protected witnesses, with hidden identities for their safety, in the terror funding case in which the National Investigation Agency (NIA) had seized around 600 electronic devices during its raids at 70 places. Malik, who had pleaded guilty for the terror funding crimes, was sentenced to life by a Delhi court. Chris Pratt and Bryce Dallas Howard are joined by OscarÂ®-winner Laura Dern, Jeff Goldblum and Sam Neill in Jurassic World Dominion, a bold, timely and breathtaking new adventure that spans the globe. |From Jurassic World architect and director Colin Trevorrow, Dominion takes place four years after Isla Nublar has been destroyed. Dinosaurs now liveâ€”and huntâ€”alongside humans all over the world. This fragile balance will reshape the future and determine, once and for all, whether human beings are to remain the apex predators on a planet they now share with historyâ€™s most fearsome creatures. |Jurassic World Dominion, from Universal Pictures and Amblin Entertainment, propels the more than $5 billion franchise into daring, uncharted territory, featuring never-seen dinosaurs, breakneck action and astonishing new visual effects. |The film features new cast members DeWanda Wise (Sheâ€™s Gotta Have It), Emmy nominee Mamoudou Athie (Archive 81), Dichen Lachman (Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.), Scott Haze (Minari) and Campbell Scott (The Amazing Spider-Man 2). The filmâ€™s returning cast includes BD Wong as Dr. Henry Wu, Justice Smith as Franklin Webb, Daniella Pineda as Dr. Zia Rodriguez and Omar Sy as Barry SembenÃ¨.  |Jurassic World Dominion is directed by Colin Trevorrow, who steered 2015â€™s Jurassic World to a record-shattering $1.7 billion global box office. The screenplay is by Emily Carmichael (Battle at Big Rock) & Colin Trevorrow from a story by Derek Connolly (Jurassic World) & Trevorrow, based on characters created by Michael Crichton. Jurassic World Dominion is produced by acclaimed franchise producers Frank Marshall p.g.a. and Patrick Crowley p.g.a. and is executive produced by legendary, OscarÂ®-winning franchise creator Steven Spielberg, Alexandra Derbyshire and Colin Trevorrow. |Universal Pictures and Amblin Entertainment present, in association with Perfect World Pictures, a Colin Trevorrow film. jurassicworld.com

Central to that journey is one of the significant and influential people in Elvisâ€™s life, Priscilla Presley (Olivia DeJonge). |Starring alongside Butler and Hanks, award-winning theatre actress Helen Thomson (â€œTop of the Lake: China Girl,â€ â€œRakeâ€) plays Elvisâ€™s mother, Gladys, Richard Roxburgh (â€œMoulin Rouge!â€ â€œBreath,â€ â€œHacksaw Ridgeâ€) portrays Elvisâ€™s father, Vernon, and DeJonge (â€œThe Visit,â€ â€œStray Dollsâ€) plays Priscilla. Luke Bracey (â€œHacksaw Ridge,â€ â€œPoint Breakâ€) plays Jerry Schilling, Natasha Bassett (â€œHail, Caesar!â€) plays Dixie Locke, David Wenham (â€œThe Lord of the Ringsâ€ Trilogy, â€œLion,â€ â€œ300â€) plays Hank Snow, Kelvin Harrison Jr. (â€œThe Trial of the Chicago 7,â€ â€œThe High Noteâ€) plays B.B. King, Xavier Samuel (â€œAdore,â€ â€œLove & Friendship,â€ â€œThe Twilight Saga: Eclipseâ€) plays Scotty Moore, and Kodi Smit-McPhee (â€œThe Power of the Dogâ€) plays Jimmie Rodgers Snow. |Also in the cast, Dacre Montgomery (â€œStranger Things,â€ â€œThe Broken Heart Galleryâ€) plays TV director Steve Binder, alongside Australian actors Leon Ford (â€œGallipoli,â€ â€œThe Pacificâ€) as Tom Diskin, Kate Mulvany (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œHuntersâ€) as Marion Keisker, Gareth Davies (â€œPeter Rabbit,â€ â€œHuntersâ€) as Bones Howe, Charles Grounds (â€œCrazy Rich Asians,â€ â€œCampâ€) as Billy Smith, Josh McConville (â€œFantasy Islandâ€) as Sam Phillips, and Adam Dunn (â€œHome and Awayâ€) as Bill Black. |To play additional iconic musical artists in the film, Luhrmann cast singer/songwriter Yola as Sister Rosetta Tharpe, model Alton Mason as Little Richard, Austin, Texas native Gary Clark Jr. as Arthur Crudup, and artist Shonka Dukureh as Willie Mae â€œBig Mamaâ€ Thornton. |Oscar nominee Luhrmann (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€) directed from a screenplay by Baz Luhrmann & Sam Bromell and Baz Luhrmann & Craig Pearce and Jeremy Doner, story by Baz Luhrmann and Jeremy Doner. The filmâ€™s producers are Luhrmann, Oscar winner Catherine Martin (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€), Gail Berman, Patrick McCormick and Schuyler Weiss. Toby Emmerich, Courtenay Valenti and Kevin McCormick executive produced. |The directorâ€™s behind-the-scenes creative team includes director of photography Mandy Walker (â€œMulan,â€ â€œAustraliaâ€), Oscar-winning production designer and costume designer Catherine Martin (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€), production designer Karen Murphy (â€œA Star Is Bornâ€), editors Matt Villa (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œAustraliaâ€) and Jonathan Redmond (â€œThe Great Gatsbyâ€), Oscar-nominated visual effects supervisor Thomas Wood (â€œMad Max: Fury Roadâ€), music supervisor Anton Monsted (â€œAustralia,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€) and composer Elliott Wheeler (â€œThe Get Downâ€). |Principal photography on â€œElvisâ€ took place in Queensland, Australia with the support of the Queensland Government, Screen Queensland, and the Australian Governmentâ€™s Producer Offset program. |A Warner Bros. Pictures Presentation, A Bazmark Production, A Jackal Group Production, A Baz Luhrmann Film, â€œElvisâ€ will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to release in theaters in North America on June 24, 2022, and internationally beginning 22 June 2022.

title: Adam Savage Stunned By This AT-AT Walker Garage Kit!
description: In Adam's past experience, small batch garage kits made by fans vary wildly in quality, and castings can often suffer from deteriorating molds of complex parts. That's not the case with this studio scale Walker garage kit Adam unboxes today--he is left speechless by the quality of these parts and detail retained in the castings. title: IAF trumps Chinese Air Force in global Air Power index; Ranks 3rd after US and Russia | Key Details
description: The Indian Air Force has been ranked the third most powerful air power in the world. According to a report published by the World Directory of Modern Military Aircraft, the IAF is better than the Chinese Air Force. The US tops the list followed by Russia. India is at the 3rd spot and China is at the 4th position. Although China has more aircraft than India but lacks in superiority. Watch this video to know more.

title: PM Modi dedicates to the nation and lays foundation stone of development initiatives in Chennai
description: PM in Chennai|In a step towards boosting infrastructure development, enhancing connectivity and giving an impetus to ease of living in the region, Prime Minister will dedicate to the nation and lay the foundation stone of 11 projects worth over Rs 31,500 crore in Chennai. These projects will also help significantly improve socio-economic prosperity in the region, have a transformative impact on several sectors and also help create employment opportunities.|In Chennai, Prime Minister will dedicate to the nation five projects worth over Rs 2960 crore. The 75 km long Madurai-Teni (Railway Gauge Conversion Project), built at a project cost of over Rs. 500 crore, will facilitate access and give a boost to tourism in the region. The 30 km long third railway line between Tambaram - Chengalpattu, built at a project cost of over Rs. 590 crore, will facilitate running of more Suburban services, thus offering greater options and enhancing comfort for the travellers.|The 115 km long Ennore-Chengalpattu section and 271 km long Thiruvallur-Bengaluru section of ETBPNMT natural gas pipeline, built at a project cost of around Rs. 850 crore and Rs 910 crore respectively, will facilitate supply of natural gas to consumers as well industries in Tamil Nadu, Karnataka and Andhra Pradesh.|The programme will also witness inauguration of 1152 houses constructed as part of Light House Project - Chennai, built at a cost of Rs 116 crore under Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana-Urban.|Prime Minister will also lay the foundation stone of six projects, being built at a cost of over Rs. 28,540 crore.|The 262 Km long Bengaluru - Chennai Expressway will be built at a cost of over Rs. 14,870 crore. It will pass-through states of Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh and Tamil Nadu and help reduce travel time between Bengaluru and Chennai by 2-3 hours. The 4 Lane double decker elevated road connecting Chennai Port to Maduravoyal (NH-4), of about 21 Km in length, will be built at a cost of over Rs 5850 crore. It will facilitate round the clock approach of goods vehicles to Chennai port. The â€‹â€‹94 km long 4 lane Neraluru to Dharmapuri section of NH-844 and 31 km long 2 lane with paved shoulders of Meensurutti to Chidambaram section of NH-227, being built at a cost of around Rs 3870 crore and Rs 720 respectively, will help provide seamless connectivity in the region.|The foundation stones for redevelopment of five Railway stations: Chennai Egmore, Rameswaram, Madurai, Katpadi and Kanniyakumari, will also be laid during the programme. This project will be completed at a cost of over Rs. 1800 crore, and is being undertaken with a view to enhance convenience and comfort of the passengers through provision of modern amenities.|Prime Minister will also lay the foundation stone of a Multi Modal Logistic Park at Chennai worth around Rs. 1430 crore. It will provide seamless intermodal freight movement and also offer multiple functionalities.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! ğŸ””||||Follow us to stay updated:||||â–º Download the NM App: http://nm4.in/dnldapp||â–º Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/narendramodi|#Chennai #TamilNadu  #BengaluruChennaiExpressway  #MultiModalLogisticPark

title: Random Hacks For Everyday Problems
description: Stay right there because you are seconds away from knowing a couple of ideas that will make your daily routine. Put a fun spin on everything you do and show your friends that you can find a creative way to solve the little problems life throws at you. You can even make a lot of crafts with products and materials that you already have at home. So get ready and tell us which ideas you will try first. title: 'Pan India Film Nothing But New Coinage': Veteran Actor Kamal Haasan On Language War In Cinema
description: Veteran actor Kamal Haasan on Thursday said the term 'pan India' film was nothing but a "new coinage" as the Indian cinema has always churned out classics such as Mughal-e-Azam and Chemeen, films that were popular across languages.|Haasan, who has worked in over 200 movies across Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam, Kannada, Hindi and Bengali film industries, said the success of a pan India project depends on its universal appeal and quality of film making.|"When you pan for gold, you pan for new words, coinages. Pan India (films) have always been there," the 67-year-old said. description: https://www.raiplay.it/programmi/report - Di Paolo Mondani, da Report del 23/05/2022. A 30 anni dalla morte di Giovanni Falcone, emergono documenti e protagonisti dimenticati in grado di gettare una nuova luce su quei fatti. A Capaci, Cosa Nostra non ha agito da sola: estremisti di destra e uomini di mafia, secondo testimoni e documenti ritrovati, sarebbero stati di nuovo insieme, dopo gli anni della strategia della tensione, in un abbraccio mortale costato la vita ai giudici Falcone e Borsellino. I due magistrati avevano il quadro completo, e oggi, tornando ad ascoltare collaboratori ed ex carabinieri, Report prova a ricostruirlo.

title: China bridge row: Indian army counters Xiâ€™s threat along LAC; Steps up military deployment
description: While China builds a second, bigger and broader bridge over the Pangong Tso, Hindustan Times has learnt that the Indian army has been deployed at the LAC to counter Peopleâ€™s Liberation Army's aggressive infrastructure development. This comes nearly a month after the new Chief of Army Staff, General Manoj Pande, conducted a security review of the Chinese PLAâ€™s positions in East Ladakh. As per HT report, the Indian Army has studied the satellite pictures of the twin Chinese bridges and found out that the first bridge built over the narrowest part of Pangong Tso at Khurnak Fort was 6m  wide. The second bridge is 11m wide and has the capacity to handle 70 tons of load, which is more than the weight of the heaviest Chinese tank. title: Momen Adik Jokowi dan Anwar Usman Bernyanyi Bareng Judika di Pelaminan
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV - Pernikahan adik kandung Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati dengan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi RI Anwar Usman berlangsung di Gedung Graha Saba Buana, Solo, Jawa Tengah, Kamis (26/5).||||Dalam acara resepsi, hadir sebagai penghibur penyanyi Judika.||||Pada kesempatan itu, tampak Idayati dan sang suami Anwar Usman bernyanyi bersama Judika di pelaminan.||||Idayati yang mengenakan gaun pengantin berwarna merah itu tampak menikmati alunan musik yang mengiringinya.||||Tak hanya Idayati, sang suami Anwar Usman turut mempersembahkan lagu untuk istri tercintanya.||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||Judika pun memuji kepiawaian Ketua MK itu dalam tarik suara. "aslinya penyanyi ternyata" kata Judika.||||Untuk diketahui, adik kandung Presiden Joko Widodo (Jokowi) dan Ketua Mahkamah Agung Anwar Usman resmi menikah, pada Kamis (26/5) di Gedung Graha Saba Buana, Solo, Jawa Tengah.||||Wali nikah pernikahan tersebut ialah Presiden Joko Widodo selaku kakak kandung Idayati.||||Sementara Wakil Presiden Maruf Amin dan Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa menjadi saksi pernikahan.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292877/momen-adik-jokowi-dan-anwar-usman-bernyanyi-bareng-judika-di-pelaminan

description: Hundreds of people have attended a vigil in Uvalde, Texas, after 19 children and two teachers were killed in a mass shooting at a primary school. |The children who died were aged between seven and 10. title: Begini Gaya Prabowo hingga Ganjar Pranowo di Nikahan Adik Jokowi
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV   Sejumlah tamu VIP tiba di pernikahan Idayati dan Anwar Usman pada Kamis (26/5/2022). ||||Selain Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa yang menjadi saksi nikah tampak juga Menko Polhukam Mahfud MD.||||Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo datang bersama sang istri, lalu disusul menhan Prabowo Subianto bersama ajudannya.||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||Acara pernikahan telah berlangsung di Gedung Graha Shaba Buana, Solo, Kamis (26/5/2022). ||||Turut hadir Wali nikah pernikahan tersebut adalah Jokowi. ||||Adapun saksi nikah yang dihadirkan ialah Wakil Presiden Ma'ruf Amin dari pihak perempuan dan Andika menjadi saksi nikah dari pihak laki-laki.||||Video Editor: Febi||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292814/begini-gaya-prabowo-hingga-ganjar-pranowo-di-nikahan-adik-jokowi

title: PM Modi attends programme on completion of 20 years of Indian School of Business, Hyderabad
description: Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi will visit Hyderabad and Chennai on 26 May 2022. At around 2 PM. Prime Minister will participate in the celebration of completion of 20 years of Indian School of Business (ISB) Hyderabad and address the graduation ceremony of Post Graduate Programme (PGP) Class of 2022. ISB was inaugurated on 2 December 2001, by Former Prime Minister Shri Atal Bihari Vajpayee. title: Trump reacted with approval to 'hang Mike Pence' chants
description: A former aide to Trump White House chief of staff Mark Meadows told the House January 6 committee that then-President Donald Trump had suggested to Meadows he approved of the "hang Mike Pence" chants from rioters who stormed the US Capitol, two sources familiar with the matter told CNN. #CNN #News

title: The Wild Story Of Michael Che's Standup Debut On David Letterman's "Late Show"
description: Michael Che makes his first visit to the Ed Sullivan Theater since his standup comedy debut on "The Late Show with David Letterman" a decade ago, and shares the truly wild story of how he got to the theater that day amid the chaos of Superstorm Sandy. title: Indian Navy hits 'bulls eye' from warship INS Teg; Surface-to-air missile system tested
description: The Indian Navy's guided-missile anti-submarine stealth frigate successfully engaged a low flying target with its surface-to-air missile (SAM) system. As per reports, the test fire took place from Talwar Class Indian Navy warship - INS Teg. The location of the test firing was not shared. "All in a days work! Watch YourNavy's guided-missile anti-submarine stealth frigate do what it does best - successfully engage a low flying target with its SAM system, reaffirming the mantra of her crew, HIT FIRST! HIT HARD! Congrats to the team for a text book bullseye!" the Indian Navy tweeted. Watch this video for more details.|#Navy #India #INSTeg #TalwarClass #SurfaceToAirMissile #SamSystem #AntiSubmarineStealthFrigate #ShtilMissile

title: Momen Presiden Jokowi jadi Wali Nikah Adiknya dengan Anwar Usman
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV -  Adik Presiden Jokowi, Idayati menikah dengan Ketua MK Anwar Usman. ||||Keduanya telah melangsungkan pernikahan di Graha Saba Buana Solo Kamis (26/5/2022).||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||"Haji anwar usman SH.MH, bin haji Suman, saya nikahkan dan saya jodohkan dengan saudari perempuan saya Idayati binti Notomiharjo nikah dengan engkau, dengan mas kawin, dengan seperangkat alat salat dan sebuah jam tangan dibayar tunai."ucap Jokowi saat menjadi wali nikah keduanya, Kamis (26/5/2022). ||||"Saya terima nikah dan jodohnya idayati binti Notomiharjo dengan mahar tersebut tunai," jawab Anwar Usman.||||Adapun saksi nikah yang dihadirkan ialah Wakil Presiden Ma'ruf Amin dari pihak perempuan dan Andika menjadi saksi nikah dari pihak laki-laki.||||Video Editor: Febi||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292764/momen-presiden-jokowi-jadi-wali-nikah-adiknya-dengan-anwar-usman

title: KIsah Cinta Ketua MK dan Adik Jokowi yang Berakhir Bahagia di Pelaminan!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Sejak masih berupa isu dan rencana hingga hari-H, pernikahan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi, Anwar Usman dan adik Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati selalu hangat diperbincangkan publik.||||Tak ada ritual pingitan yang dijalani Anwar Usman dan Idayati, seperti pasangan calon pengantin Jawa pada umumnya.||||Dengan jadwal yang padat, Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi dan adik Presiden Joko Widodo ini justru seharian menghabiskan waktu bersama menjelang pernikahan mereka.||||Rabu (25/5/2022) pagi, keduanya menggelar acara pengajian bersama-sama di rumah almarhumah ibunda Jokowi dan Idayati, Sujiatmi Notomiharjo di Solo, Jawa Tengah.||||Baca Juga Usai Hadiri Nikahan Adik, Jokowi Blusukan ke Taman Balekambang dan Pasar Mojosongo di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292789/usai-hadiri-nikahan-adik-jokowi-blusukan-ke-taman-balekambang-dan-pasar-mojosongo||||Rabu (25/5/2022) sore, Anwar dan Idayati juga hadir langsung dalam acara gladi bersih prosesi pernikahan keduanya.||||Siapapun yang hadir di Graha Saba Buana sore itu, pasti bisa melihat binar mata penuh cinta dan bahagia yang terpancar dari raut wajah mereka.||||Di balik segala kontroversinya, pihak keluarga tetap mendukung keputusan Anwar untuk mempersunting Idayati.||||Ketulusan cinta Anwar Usman kepada Idayati juga dirasakan oleh Wedding Organizer yang membidani acara pernikahan ini.||||Tak banyak pasangan berusia lanjut yang begitu mantap melanjutkan ke jenjang pernikahan, memutuskan hidup bersama sambil mengasuh anak cucu mereka.||||Selamat menempuh hidup baru Ibu Idayati dan Pak Anwar Usman,||semoga selalu langgeng dan berbahagia.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292795/kisah-cinta-ketua-mk-dan-adik-jokowi-yang-berakhir-bahagia-di-pelaminan

title: Suzuki Vision Gran Turismo : Unveiled
description: On May 26, 2022, the 'Suzuki Vision Gran Turismo' was introduced in the 1.15 update of Gran Turismo 7.|Suzuki is one of the rare manufacturers of the world who are known to produce both 4 wheel and 2 wheel vehicles. Their 'Suzuki Vision Gran Turismo' is a fusion of the sporting mindset that flows in their 4 wheel and 2 wheel machines, developed as a unique all-wheel drive supersport.|Powered by a front midship mounted inline 4 engine from their flagship 'Hayabusa' sports bike, this is a VGT based on the midship sportscar 'GSX-R/4' concept model announced in 2001, updated with the latest tech to bring it back as an all-wheel drive super sport overflowing with the sporting mindset of the brand. |We hope you enjoy the world of pure sport as presented by Suzuki.|Vision Gran Turismo is a project in which the worldâ€™s leading automotive brands design new sports cars that are then offered as gifts to Gran Turismo players. title: Kisah Nyata Dewi Perssik - Antara Restu Ibu atau Suamiku
description: Tonton tayangan lengkap Indosiar di vidio.com atau klik https://www.vidio.com/watch/1523256-sinema-indosiar-antara-restu-ibu-atau-suamiku|Sudah 5 tahun menikah namun Ana (Dewi Perssik) belum juga hamil. Akhirnya, Robi (Panji Saputra) meminta Ana untuk berhenti bekerja dan fokus pada program kehamilannya. Sebaliknya, Ibunya Ana (Mutia Datau) menginginkan Ana untuk tetap bekerja agar tidak hanya mengekor pada suami dan juga bisa membiayai keluarganya. Ana bingung dan berada dalam situasi terjepit untuk memilih antara ibunya atau Robi. Bagaimana kisah selanjutnya? Saksikan selengkapnya hanya di Sinema Indosiar - Antara Restu Ibu atau Suamiku, dimainkan Mutia Datau, Panji Saputra, Dewi Perssik, dan lainnya. title: Stadium Emptied, Athletes Told To Leave, For IAS Officer To Walk With Dog

title: 'I believe the PM has lied repeatedly, knowingly' says Chair of Commons Standards Committee
description: Chair of Commons Standards Committee Chris Bryant has said he believes the Prime Minister "has lied repeatedly" and "knowingly", following the publication of a report into lockdown-breaking parties at Downing Street. |Mr Bryant said "the lockdown rules didn't say anywhere about work events, they simply said no gatherings were allowed, and these were gatherings and the PM was at them."|Mr Bryant has recused himself from the Commons Standards Committee, which could call for the Prime Minister's suspension from the House from anywhere between "one and ten days" should they find he mislead parliament.|#Partygate #BorisJohnson #SkyNews|SUBSCRIBE to our YouTube channel for more videos: http://www.youtube.com/skynews |Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/skynews |Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/skynews |Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/skynews |Follow us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@skynews|For more content go to http://news.sky.com and download our apps: |Apple: https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/sky-news/id316391924?mt=8 |Android https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bskyb.skynews.android&hl=en_GB |Sky News videos are now available in Spanish here/Los video de Sky News estÃ¡n disponibles en espaÃ±ol aquÃ­ https://www.youtube.com/channel/skynewsespanol|Sky News videos are also available in German here/Hier kÃ¶nnen Sie auÃŸerdem Sky News-Videos auf Deutsch finden: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHYg31l2xrF-Bj859nsOfnA|To enquire about licensing Sky News content, you can find more information here:  https://news.sky.com/info/library-sales

title: 2 On Your Side: Homeowner locked out by tenant who is accused of illegally subletting the home
description: Kristine Lazar reports on a San Fernando Valley homeowner who purchased his home last summer, but has been unable to move in because a tenant who lived there when he bought it has refused to leave, had the locks changed and is accused of illegally subletting the home.

title: Bukan Tokoh Politik, Ini Mak Comblang Sang Ketua MK dan Adik Presiden Jokowi
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV - Di balik segala kontroversinya, pihak keluarga tetap mendukung keputusan Anwar untuk mempersunting Idayati.||||Meski kisah asmara mereka bergerak begitu cepat dalam senyap menuju jenjang pernikahan, ternyata ada sosok mak comblang penting yang mempertemukan keduanya pada Oktober 2021 lalu.||||Ketulusan cinta Anwar Usman kepada Idayati, juga dirasakan oleh "wedding organizer" yang membidangi acara pernikahan ini.||||Tak banyak pasangan berusia lanjut yang begitu mantap melanjutkan ke jenjang pernikahan memutuskan hidup bersama sambil mengasuh anak cucu mereka.||||Anwar Usman menjadi duda setelah ditinggal sang istri, Suhada Binti Ahmad Sidik yang wafat karena sakit pada Februari 2021 lalu.||||Sementara Idayati, juga ditinggal wafat suaminya, Hari Mulyono sejak 2018.||||Dari pernikahan sebelumnya, Anwar memiliki tiga orang anak, sementara Idayati punya dua orang anak yang kini masing-masing juga sudah berkeluarga.||||Pada Haro Kamis, 26 Mei 2022 Gedung Graha Saba Buana sekali lagi menjadi saksi bisu momen sakral pernikahan keluarga Presiden Joko Widodo.||||Ada 200 tamu akad nikah serta 800 orang tamu resepsi yang dijaga ketat oleh lebih dari dua ribu personel gabungan TNI dan Polisi.||||Selamat menempuh hidup baru,  Ibu Idayati dan Pak Anwar Usman.||||Semoga selalu langgeng dan berbahagia. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292755/bukan-tokoh-politik-ini-mak-comblang-sang-ketua-mk-dan-adik-presiden-jokowi

title: Yunarto: Presiden Membuka Ruang Komunikasi Dengan Tema Yang Jelas - SATU MEJA
description: OMPASTV - Presiden Jokowi dianggap memberi sinyal dukungan untuk Ganjar Pranowo. Kode itu dilempar Jokowi dalam acara Rakernas V Projo. Kalimat "mungkin yang kita dukung ada di sini" dianggap sebagai restu dan dukungan Jokowi untuk gubernur Jawa Tengah ini.||||Ganjar memang digadang-gadang menjadi salah satu calon yang berpeluang maju di Pemilihan Presiden (Pilpres) 2024 mendatang. Meski belum direstui PDIP, hasil survei berbagai lembaga terkait bursa capres menempatkan Ganjar sebagai salah satu tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi selain Prabowo Subianto.||||Benarkah Jokowi mendukung Ganjar Pranowo untuk maju di Pilpres 2024 nanti? Lalu bagaimana PDI Perjuangan menyikapi manuver Jokowi ini? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "MEMBACA SINYAL JOKOWI" Rabu, 25 Mei 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB di Kompas TV bersama jurnalis senior Harian Kompas, Budiman Tanuredjo.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292750/yunarto-presiden-membuka-ruang-komunikasi-dengan-tema-yang-jelas-satu-meja

title: Jazilul Fawaid: Elektoral Ganjar Yang Tinggi Karena Ada Jokowi - SATU MEJA
description: KOMPASTV - Presiden Jokowi dianggap memberi sinyal dukungan untuk Ganjar Pranowo. Kode itu dilempar Jokowi dalam acara Rakernas V Projo. Kalimat "mungkin yang kita dukung ada di sini" dianggap sebagai restu dan dukungan Jokowi untuk gubernur Jawa Tengah ini.||||Ganjar memang digadang-gadang menjadi salah satu calon yang berpeluang maju di Pemilihan Presiden (Pilpres) 2024 mendatang. Meski belum direstui PDIP, hasil survei berbagai lembaga terkait bursa capres menempatkan Ganjar sebagai salah satu tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi selain Prabowo Subianto.||||Benarkah Jokowi mendukung Ganjar Pranowo untuk maju di Pilpres 2024 nanti? Lalu bagaimana PDI Perjuangan menyikapi manuver Jokowi ini? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "MEMBACA SINYAL JOKOWI" Rabu, 25 Mei 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB di Kompas TV bersama jurnalis senior Harian Kompas, Budiman Tanuredjo.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292751/jazilul-fawaid-elektoral-ganjar-yang-tinggi-karena-ada-jokowi-satu-meja

title: Membaca Sinyal Jokowi - SATU MEJA
description: KOMPASTV - Presiden Jokowi dianggap memberi sinyal dukungan untuk Ganjar Pranowo. Kode itu dilempar Jokowi dalam acara Rakernas V Projo. Kalimat "mungkin yang kita dukung ada di sini" dianggap sebagai restu dan dukungan Jokowi untuk gubernur Jawa Tengah ini.||||Ganjar memang digadang-gadang menjadi salah satu calon yang berpeluang maju di Pemilihan Presiden (Pilpres) 2024 mendatang. Meski belum direstui PDIP, hasil survei berbagai lembaga terkait bursa capres menempatkan Ganjar sebagai salah satu tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi selain Prabowo Subianto.||||Benarkah Jokowi mendukung Ganjar Pranowo untuk maju di Pilpres 2024 nanti? Lalu bagaimana PDI Perjuangan menyikapi manuver Jokowi ini? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "MEMBACA SINYAL JOKOWI" Rabu, 25 Mei 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB di Kompas TV bersama jurnalis senior Harian Kompas, Budiman Tanuredjo.|||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292748/membaca-sinyal-jokowi-satu-meja

title: Fakta Menarik Tempat Pernikahan Adik Jokowi dan Ketua MK Anwar Usman
description: KOMPAS.TV- Pernikahan Idayati dan Anwar Usman berlangsung di Gedung Graha Saba Buana, Sumber, Banjarsari, Kota Surakarta, Jawa Tengah.||||Ternyata tempat pernikahan adik Jokowi dan Ketua MK ini menyimpan sederet fakta menarik, apa saja?||||Menyadur dari Kompas.tv berikut informasinya:||||Nama Graha Saba Buana||||Nama Graha Saba Buana mempunyai arti khusus pada kata terakhirnya yakni Buana.||||Kata ini gabungan dari dua suku kata yakni bu, dan ana ana sendiri merupakan kependekan dari Iriana.||||Hadiah Ulang Tahun dari Jokowi untuk Iriana||||Gedung ini diberikan tahun 2002 untuk kegiatan Iriana saat ditinggal Jokowi bertugas.||||Daya Tampung Graha Saba Buana||||Gedung ini seluas 4000m persegi dan mampu menampung 2000 orang sementara untuk kendaraan dapat memuat sekiranya 300 mobil.||||Desain Interior Klasik||||Graha Saba Buana berdesain interior unik dengan nuansa Jawa Klasik yang kental.||||Diskon Khusus Tetangga||||Diskon yang diberikan sebesar 20% , namun diskon ini hanya untuk tetangga satu RT dengan Jokowi.||||Baca Juga Momen Tamu VIP Kabinet Indonesia Maju Berdatangan ke Pernikahan Adik Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292744/momen-tamu-vip-kabinet-indonesia-maju-berdatangan-ke-pernikahan-adik-jokowi||||Editor Video & Grafis: Arief Rahman ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292813/fakta-menarik-tempat-pernikahan-adik-jokowi-dan-ketua-mk-anwar-usman

title: Andika Perkasa Angkat Bicara Soal Namanya Diduetkan Bareng Ganjar Pranowo di 2024
description: SLEMAN, KOMPAS.TV - Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa angkat bicara soal namanya yang diduetkan dengan Ganjar Pranowo untuk Pilpres 2024.||||Menanggapi hal itu, Andika mengucapkan terima kasih atas dukungan yang diberikan banyak pihak. Andika menyebut dukungan itu sebagai bentuk kepercayaan dari banyak orang, baik untuk pribadinya maupun institusi TNI.||||Namun Andika menegaskan saat ini dirinya akan fokus bekerja sebagai panglima TNI terlebih dahulu hingga masa jabatannya selesai.||||Baca Juga Andika Perkasa Ungkap Anggota TNI Terlibat Kasus Kerangkeng Manusia di Langkat Bisa Bertambah di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292716/andika-perkasa-ungkap-anggota-tni-terlibat-kasus-kerangkeng-manusia-di-langkat-bisa-bertambah||||Diketahui, nama Panglima TNI Jendral Andika Perkasa menjadi salah satu yang disebut-sebut layak diduetkan dengan Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo dalam pemilu Presiden 2024 mendatang.||||Bahkan di Yogyakarta muncul sekelompok orang yang mengatasnamakan relawan Ganjar-Perkasa.||||Terkait munculnya relawan Ganjar-Perkasa ini, Andika pun mengaku belum pernah dipertemukan secara khusus dengan Ganjar untuk membicarakan duet calon pada pemilu Presiden 2024 mendatang.||||Video Editor: Ian Andrian||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292754/andika-perkasa-angkat-bicara-soal-namanya-diduetkan-bareng-ganjar-pranowo-di-2024

title: SAH! Ketua MK Anwar Usman Resmi Jadi Suami Idayati, Adik Presiden Jokowi
description: SOLO, KOMPAS.TV - Akad nikah adik Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati dengan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi, Anwar Usman berlangsung khidmat.||||Ijab qobul, Idayati dan Anwar Usman berlangsung pukul 10.00 pagi tadi di Graha Saba Buana, Banjarsari, Solo, Jawa Tengah.||||Rangkaian prosesi akad nikah sebelumnya diiringi alunan gamelan di gedung yang didekorasi dengan nuansa Jawa klasik.||||Baca Juga Usung Adat Jawa Klasik, Ini Makna Dekorasi Pelaminan Adik Jokowi dan Ketua MK di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292757/usung-adat-jawa-klasik-ini-makna-dekorasi-pelaminan-adik-jokowi-dan-ketua-mk||||Sejak Kamis (26/5/2022) pagi, sesuai adat tradisi Jawa, tahap pertama dilakukan prosesi pasrah tampi atau menyerahkan mempelai laki-laki kepada keluarga mempelai perempuan.||||Setelah diterima oleh keluarga mempelai perempuan, mempelai laki-laki langsung ke meja akad nikah, Presiden Jokowi sebagai wali nikah mempelai perempuan dan berlaku sebagai saksi Panglima TNI Jendral Andhika Perkasa dan Wakil Presiden, Ma'ruf Amin.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292767/sah-ketua-mk-anwar-usman-resmi-jadi-suami-idayati-adik-presiden-jokowi

title: Siapa Sebenarnya Idayati Adik Presiden Jokowi dan Anwar Usman Ketua MK yang Menikah? Ini Profilnya
description: KOMPAS.TV - Adik Presiden Joko Widodo, Idayati, Kamis 26 Mei 2022 dipersunting oleh Anwar Usman yang merupakan Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi.||||Surakarta Jawa Tengah dipilih menjadi tempat akad nikah dan resepsi.||||Idayati adalah adik kedua Jokowi yang lahir pada 26 Mei 1966 di Solo Jawa Tengah.||||Ia memiliki dua anak dari pernikahan pertamanya, yaitu Septiara Silvani Putri dan Rimbo Galih Samudra.||||Sehari-hari ia merupakan ibu rumah tangga dan menetap di Solo||||Lalu siapakah sosok Anwar Usman yang mempersunting adik orang nomor satu di Indonesia ini?||||Mengutip Laman Mahkamah Konstitusi  Anwar lahir dan dibesarkan di Desa Rasabou, Kecamatan Bolo, Bima, Nusa Tenggara Barat.||||Pria kelahiran 65 tahun silam itu mengawali kariernya sebagai guru honorer pada 1975.||||Setelah lulus dari SDN 03 Sil, Bima pada tahun 1969, ia melanjutkan pendidikannya di Sekolah Pendidikan Guru Agama Negeri atau PGAN selama enam tahun hingga 1975.||||Pada perjalanan kariernya di lembaga peradilan Anwar Usman sempat menjabat sebagai Wakil Ketua MK untuk dua periode.||||Selepas itu, Usman juga diangkat menjadi Ketua Mahkamah Konstitusi dengan masa jabatan dua periode.||||Periode pertama pada 6 April 2011-6 April 2016 dan periode kedua 6 April 2016-6 April 2026. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292721/siapa-sebenarnya-idayati-adik-presiden-jokowi-dan-anwar-usman-ketua-mk-yang-menikah-ini-profilnya

title: 'India's interests...': Piyush Goyal hits back at the West over Russian energy imports
description: Union Commerce Minister Piyush Goyal has trashed the criticism of Western countries over Russian imports. Speaking at World Economic Forum, Goyal countered the West saying that India takes decisions as per its national interest. He also rejected the charge that India has contributed to the rise in Russian exports amid Ukraine War. title: Global National: May 25, 2022 | Agony and anger rise in aftermath of Uvalde, Texas school shooting
description: The city of Uvalde, Texas is in despair after a gunman shot and killed 19 children and two teachers, in what is now the second deadliest U.S. school shooting. Jackson Proskow reports on who the victims are, the devastating grief overwhelming their families, and the anger politicians are facing once again over another senseless mass shooting.|The school shooting is also forcing many people to revisit America's past school shootings, especially the December 2012 massacre at Sandy Hook Elementary School. While it and every other mass shooting has spawned calls for tighter gun control in the U.S., Eric Sorensen explains how gun reform has been an uphill battle.|As Ottawa cleans up from a vicious storm, now volunteers are doing what they can to help residents left in the dark. David Akin visits some of the hardest-hit neighbourhoods in the nation's capital to see how people are coping.|Concerns are growing about the global outbreak of the monkeypox virus, as more cases are confirmed in Canada. Dan Spector looks at where infections are being detected, the push for vaccinations, and how health experts are urging calm.|In the U.K., a critical independent report has been released on British Prime Minister Boris Johnson's multiple boozy parties which broke pandemic rules. And as Crystal Goomansingh reports, 'Teflon Boris' has earned his nickname as he remains in office.|One year after the revelation of unmarked graves at the former Kamloops Indigenous Residential School in British Columbia, the Tk'emlÃºps te SecwÃ©pemc First Nation is preparing to exhume the hundreds of remains found at the facility. title: Boeing #Starliner Spacecraft Deorbit Burn and Landing (Official NASA Broadcast)
description: Watch the landing of Boeing's uncrewed Starliner, targeted at 6:49 p.m. EDT (22:49 UTC) at White Sands Space Harbor at the U.S. Armyâ€™s White Sands Missile Range in New Mexico. This return to Earth will wrap up the six-day Orbital Flight Test-2, which will provide valuable data toward NASA certifying Boeingâ€™s crew transportation system for regular flights with astronauts to and from the International Space Station.  |Boeing's Starliner launched to the space station on Thursday, May 19 aboard a United Launch Alliance Atlas V rocket, and docked to the orbiting laboratory on Friday, May 20. The crew opened Starliner's hatch on Saturday, May 21. The spacecraft will return home with more than 600 pounds of cargo, including Nitrogen Oxygen Recharge System reusable tanks that provide breathable air to station crew members. The tanks will be refurbished on Earth and sent back to station on a future flight.|Image Credit: ESA/NASA

title: Role of western intelligence under scrutiny, scale of release 'unprecedented' | DW News
description: The United States and its NATO allies have stated publicly that they're providing Ukraine with satellite images, intercepting Russian communications and helping to defend Ukraine from Russian cyber-attacks. But leaks and statements from within the US intelligence community are now claiming even closer involvement - like with the sinking of the Russian missile cruiser Moskva. The ship was struck by Ukrainian missiles, but there are reports the US provided information about its location. |This month the New York Times reported that the US had provided intelligence that helped Ukraine kill several Russian generals on the front lines. |00:00 Scale of intelligence release 'unprecedented'|00:40 Dmitri Alperovitch, cyber-policy and security expert|03:37 Russian oligarch's assets to rebuild Ukraine? |The EU Commission is moving to confiscate and sell â€” rather than simply freeze â€” the assets of Russian oligarchs. According to the EU, Russian assets worth 10 billion euros have already been frozen. Many in Brussels now say the money gained by confiscating the assets could be used to help rebuild Ukraine. Moss adds that Depp tended to her after her fall and ensured she received medical aid.

title: Stephen Curry Named To All-NBA Second Team!
description: Golden State Warriors guard Stephen Curry has been named to a franchise-record eighth All-NBA Team, the NBA announced today. It marks the third Second Team honor for Curry (First Team, four times and Third Team, once). | |Curry earned Second Team honors after averaging 25.5 points, 5.2 rebounds and 6.3 assists in 34.6 minutes per game over 64 games (all starts). He led the league in made 3-point baskets (285) for the seventh time of his career and surpassed Ray Allen (2,973) as the NBAâ€™s all-time 3-point leader. He became the fourth player in NBA history to become a franchiseâ€™s all-time leader in points, assists, 3-pointers, steals and games played.  The 13th year guard was named the 2022 NBA All-Star Game Kobe Bryant MVP along with being tabbed the NBAâ€™s Western Conference Player of the Month for games played in October and November and the leagueâ€™s Week 1 and Week 4 Western Conference Player of the Week.

title: 'You are doing nothing!': Beto O'Rourke confronts Gov. Greg Abbott at Uvalde shooting presser
description: A Wednesday press conference from Texas Republican leadership about the statewide response to Tuesday's school shooting in Uvalde, Texas, was interrupted as Democratic gubernatorial candidate Beto O'Rourke got into a heated exchange with Texas Gov. Greg Abbott, Lt. Gov. Dan Patrick, Texas House Speaker Rep. Dade Phelan and more about a lack of legislative activity to prevent such tragedies.|Some 15 minutes into the conference that started shortly after 12:30 p.m. local time, O'Rourke approached the stage in the Uvalde High Auditorium hosting the event to vocally and openly question Abbott's commitment to enacting change.|STORY: https://www.wfaa.com/article/news/special-reports/uvalde-school-shooting/beto-orourke-crashes-texas-gov-greg-abbott-uvalde-school-shooting-press-conference-demands-change/287-e0e28a87-99a6-4eda-8c81-0f8678991281|FULL UVALDE COVERAGE: https://www.wfaa.com/uvalde

title: Viral: Texas shooter sprays bullets inside school; Anxious parents cry outside for their children
description: Viral video Desperation turned to heart-wrenching sorrow for families of grade schoolers killed after an 18-year-old gunman barricaded himself in their Texas classroom and began shooting, killing at least 19 children and their two teachers. By Wednesday morning, many were left with the grim reality of an unimaginable horror as the names of the young victims of Tuesday's shooting at Robb Elementary School in the southwestern town of Uvalde began to emerge. Watch this video for more.

title: What Sue Grayâ€™s partygate report means for Boris Johnson - BBC News
description: UK PM Boris Johnson has dismissed calls to resign after Sue Gray's report found that Downing Street staff partied while the rest of the nation was in lockdown with their bosses' approval.|Ms Gray, a senior civil servant, said many events "should not have been allowed" and the PM and his officials "must bear responsibility for this culture".|Her report highlights excessive drinking, with staff being sick, and abuse of cleaning and security staff.|Boris Johnson told MPs he took "full responsibility for everything that took place on my watch", had been "humbled by the whole experience" and had learned lessons.|The BBCâ€™s Ros Atkins explains what the reportâ€™s findings mean for the prime minister.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BorisJohnson #UK #BBCNews

title: Elvis Review
description: Baz Luhrmann's Elvis is a dizzying and at times even overwhelming chronicle of the rock icon. Austin Butler is stellar as Elvis, giving it his absolute all in every scene. Tom Hanks cleverly plays against type as the manipulative and greedy Colonel Parker. While the supporting cast isn't given as many dimensions as they could have been in say, a TV miniseries, Luhrmann tells Presley's story on a grand scale suited only for the big screen, delivering an epic yet intimate maelstrom of emotions, music, ideas, and eye candy. The film's breathless pacing may befit the fevered lifestyle of a rock star, but it can also rush through necessary moments of dramatic reflection. Baz Luhrmann's Elvis is a wild ride clearly made with a big hunk o' love for its subject, and that zeal for capturing Presley's humanity, both by its director and its star, outweighs the film's excesses and shortcomings in the end. Elvis made its world premiere at the Cannes Film Festival. It opens in theaters on June 24, 2022.|#IGN #Movies

title: Russian forces focus on eastern Donbas region | DW News
description: Heavy fighting has been reported in and around the industrial city of Severodonetsk - where the regional governor says at least 12 people have been killed in shelling. Moscow says it will continue its offensive until it achieves its goals. |00:00  Russia steps up attacks on eastern Donbas |01:53 Russian firepower in Kramatorsk|04:51 Governor of Luhansk Oblast, Serhiy Haidai|05:47 Why are some people not evacuating? |Governor of Luhansk Oblast: Chances for citizens' evacuation 'are getting less and less'|"The chances [of evacuating citizens from Severodonetsk and Lysychansk] are getting less and less because the road is under fire. â€¦ We have been able to evacuate more than 40,000 people so far. Many left on their own. Those who remain in their houses are doing so exclusively at their own will," Serhiy Volodymyrovych Haidai, the governor of Luhansk Oblast in Ukraine, told DW.|"We are evacuating people but we do not deport people. But whenever there are people who want to leave we will evacuate them. Even if there are just ten people who want to leave we will try to take them out. They are our citizens. They are Ukrainians," the governor said. On allegations that Ukrainian authorities are abandoning the last two cities under Ukrainian control in Luhansk Oblast: "If we continue to evacuate them, if doctors are still working there, if we continue supplying them with drinking water, who can say that we have abandoned them? â€¦ The people who are staying there are exposing everybody to danger: themselves and the people who keep bringing them water, medicine and food."|Haidai: "We are witnessing the Russian army completely destroying Sievierodonetsk. They are shelling the whole place and they don't care whether there are civilians or whether there is a hospital or a school. They are destroying all the buildings."|The governor said the region is in need of more weapons: "Long-range artillery is what we are lacking most. We need howitzers, artillery and self-propelled systems like the French Caesar howitzers or the M777 from America. These are needed to keep the enemy at a distance and to beat them."|On whether military tactics in the regions endanger civilians, Haidai said: "We will defend ourselves. This is our land. If a city is a fortress, we will use this fortress militarily. Unfortunately the Russians don't allow civilians to leave. What shall we do? Give up? No Ukrainian will ever give up."|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Donbas #Luhansk #Evacuation

description: Go to http://squarespace.com/Chelsea & save 10% off your first website or domain with code â€œChelsea"|Our Portraits for Pros class: http://northrup.photo |The camera industry is changing, the photography industry is changing, and professional photographers are struggling. description: ChessBase 16 + Mega Database 2022: https://chessbase.in/online-shop#!/ChessBase-16-Mega-Database-2022-Combo/p/408893077|The all new Opening encyclopaeida 2022 - best way to learn openings: https://chessbase.in/online-shop#!/Opening-Encyclopaedia-2022/p/459712673|ChessBase India Premium Chess Set: https://chessbase.in/online-shop#!/ChessBase-India-Premium-Chess-Set/p/376637361/category=115044019|Chess course - A great way to learn chess from basics: https://chessbase.in/online-shop#!/~/search/keyword=Praful%20Zaveri|The Chessable Masters is the 4th of 9 events on the $1.6 million 2022 Meltwater Champions Chess Tour and takes place on chess24 from May 19-26. World Chess Champion Magnus Carlsen tops the 16-player field, which will be cut in half by the 4-day round-robin Prelims. The total prize fund is $150,000, with $750 for a win and $250 for a draw in the Prelims. The quarterfinals and semi-finals are 1-day, 4-game matches, while the final will feature two such matches over two days. The players have 15 minutes for all their moves, plus a 10-second increment starting from move 1. In the Prelims there are 3 points for a win and 1 for a draw. If a tiebreak is required the players will play two 5+3 games and then, if needed, a single Armageddon game, where White has 5 minutes to Black's 4, but a draw counts as a win for Black. title: Why There's A Cutout On The Side Of iPhone
description: Starting with iPhone 12, Apple added this rounded cutout on the side of every model. But they didnâ€™t explain what it was or why it existed. Many assumed it would be for the Apple Pencil. Since it looked similar to a cutout included on the iPad that allows the second generation Apple Pencil to magnetically attach and charge. But the iPhone doesnâ€™t support Apple Pencil. So why did Apple add this cutout to iPhone?

title: Transporter-5 Mission
description: On Wednesday, May 25 at 2:35 p.m. ET, Falcon 9 launched the Transporter-5, SpaceXâ€™s fifth dedicated smallsat rideshare program mission, from Space Launch Complex 40 at Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Florida. This was the eighth launch and landing of this Falcon 9 stage booster, which previously supported launch of Crew-1, Crew-2, SXM-8, CRS-23, IXPE, one Starlink mission, and Transporter-4. Following stage separation, SpaceX landed Falcon 9â€™s first stage on Landing Zone 1 (LZ-1) at Cape Canaveral Space Force Station.|On board this flight were 59 spacecraft, including including CubeSats, microsats, non-deploying hosted payloads, and orbital transfer vehicles.

title: Ellen Almost Gave Her Writer the Medal of Freedom by Accident
description: Ellen explained how her writer Troy almost ended up with her prestigious Medal of Freedom, which was locked in a safe. Ellen also said a fond goodbye to her producer Andy Zenor's famous short shorts and immortalized them on stage forever.

title: Exclusive Footage of Ellen's Test Shows with Tom Hanks & Helen Hunt
description: Twenty years ago, Ellen did test shows in her living room with hopes of becoming a full-fledged production. Check out how The Ellen Show started with her first guests, Tom Hanks, Helen Hunt, and Alanis Morissette.

But what begins as a journey of healing jolts into a fearsome fight for survival when a lion, a survivor of blood-thirsty poachers who now sees all humans as the enemy, begins stalking them. |Iyana Halley (The Hate U Give, This is Us series) plays Danielsâ€™ 18-year-old daughter, Meredith, and Leah Sava Jeffries (Rel series, Empire series) plays his 13-year-old, Norah.  |From visceral, experiential filmmaker Baltasar KormÃ¡kur, the director of Everest and Universal Picturesâ€™ 2 Guns and Contraband, Beast is produced by Will Packer, the blockbuster producer of Girls Trip, the Ride Along franchise, and ten movies that have opened No. 1 at the U.S. box office, including Night School, No Good Deed and Think Like a Man, by James Lopez, president of Will Packer Productions, and by Baltasar KormÃ¡kur.
